{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1030421,"duration_api_ms":699194,"num_turns":78,"result":"Done. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n## i18n Fallback Fix for PublicMenu (S97)\n\n### Problem\nRaw i18n keys (e.g. `order_status.status_new`, `loyalty.points`) were visible to guests on `/x` when translations were missing for the selected language, especially KK.\n\n### Root Cause\nThe `t()` function from `useI18n()` returns the raw key when no translation exists. There was no fallback mechanism — ~80+ `t()` calls had no protection.\n\n### Solution\n**1. `I18N_FALLBACKS` map** (90+ keys) — centralized RU fallback text for every i18n key used in PublicMenu, including child components (CheckoutView, MenuView, etc.)\n\n**2. `makeSafeT(rawT)` wrapper** — intercepts `t()` returns, detects raw key passthrough, substitutes from fallback map. Supports `{param}` interpolation in fallbacks.\n\n**3. Wrapped in X()** — `const t = makeSafeT(rawT)` ensures all child components receiving `t` as prop automatically get safe behavior.\n\n### Changes\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `x.jsx` | Added `I18N_FALLBACKS` + `makeSafeT()`, wrapped `t` |\n| `x.jsx` | Removed 7 `\\|\\| 'hardcoded'` fallback patterns |\n| `x.jsx` | Fixed hardcoded `<DrawerTitle>Корзина</DrawerTitle>` |\n| `MenuView.jsx` | Removed 3 `\\|\\| 'hardcoded'` fallback patterns |\n\n### Findings written to\n`cc-analysis-task-260307-204052.txt` — 5 findings (2x P1, 3x P2)","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"81dea0b4-8b02-4d93-bb4b-0a6c0fd24834","total_cost_usd":3.609350449999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":6061,"cache_creation_input_tokens":134438,"cache_read_input_tokens":3652302,"output_tokens":23096,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":134438},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":6061,"output